quran[22]{c,v,t}:
  54,50,"And Our command is but one, like the twinkling of an eye"
  54,51,"And We indeed destroyed sects (like those of) yours, but is there anyone who will mind"
  54,52,"And everything they did, is in the books"
  54,53,and everything small or great is written down (recorded)
  54,54,Those who guard (against evil) will certainly be in gardens with rivers
  54,55,"in a confirmed seat, near the King, the Holder of power"
  55,1,The Beneficent
  55,2,He taught the Quran
  55,3,He created man
  55,4,"He taught him to express (by action, speech, writing etc)"
  55,5,The sun and the moon (function) according to a calculation
  55,6,And the herbs and the trees bow down (to Him)
  55,7,"And the sky, He has raised it, and He has set the balance"
  55,8,"(by ordering) that: Do not exceed (the limits) in the balance"
  55,9,and establish the balance in a just manner and do not reduce the balance
  55,10,And the earth He has layed down for the cattle (living beings)
  55,11,Therein are fruits and palm trees (with) sheathed (dates)
  55,12,and grains with husk and the scented herb
  55,13,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny
  55,14,"He created man from mud, like (that used in) pottery"
  55,15,And He created the jinn from (the heat wave) let free from fire
  55,16,So which of the bounties of your Fosterer will you both deny